                     <interp inst="t18520816-781-offence-1" type="offenceSubcategory" value="simpleLarceny"></interp>, stealing 3 bonnets, 1 bonnet shape, and 1 cap, value 15<hi rend="italic">s</hi>.; the goods of <persName id="t18520816-name-84" type="victimName">
                        <interp inst="t18520816-name-84" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18520816-name-84" type="surname" value="DEACON"></interp>
