                  </hi>. I know the prisoner—I was present at Clerkenwell Sessions on 6th Nov., 1849, when she was tried for stealing two stockings, value 9<hi rend="italic">d</hi>.—she had three months—she has also been summarily convicted of stealing an image.</p>
